{"tid":1174072,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"今年超級巨聲班人係咪開始接舊人班？","createTime":"2019-05-27T14:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T05:06:20.000Z","uid":37358,"like":47,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"91cb321dec8131b6b90e8f002cd87209b7afad8b","tid":1174072,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T14:19:28.000Z","msg":"馮允謙首「山旮旯」都有幾多人留意，同埋佢個唱腔無咁ABC，順耳咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n許廷鏗可以喺華納做自己鍾意嘅音樂，雖然我覺得佢仲未好摸索到佢應該做咩類型嘅音樂，但至少佢都可以嘗試一啲新嘅可能性<br />\n<br />\n林欣彤就轉咗新公司，啱啱出個首新歌都好多正評，斷估華納呢排女歌手啲資源都會谷晒俾佢，上一線比以前好似容易咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就連陳慧敏浮浮沉沉咗幾年，最近出個首「沉默之間」連陳奕迅都推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勢估唔到超級巨聲呢個19節目可以造到咁多有力上一線嘅歌手出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a7c8fbbccd230e78a2a628561897c95d1eeb17","tid":1174072,"uid":147233,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T14:28:25.000Z","msg":"只要有人肯繼續唱廣東歌都應該要支持"},{"pid":"bd561d5297627ced827c5e44d4057922ea385b16","tid":1174072,"uid":55800,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T14:31:35.000Z","msg":"呢班人係唱得有料，只係個節目濕鳩搞到成件事柒曬，連帶佢地都霉足咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629bb78f26d4a52b12c3a53a9e75dd4f498ec57b","tid":1174072,"uid":2319,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"仲有小巧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b348341c725f7cce597597d9d4586bc276ff04","tid":1174072,"uid":54528,"like":6,"dislike":13,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T14:55:04.000Z","msg":"但真係無好歌, 又無星味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede2faf95696078465c7bf9f8157dbb7dde86a4a","tid":1174072,"uid":55280,"like":23,"dislike":0,"sc